flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{One filename argument?}
    B -- No --> C[Print usage and exit]
    B -- Yes --> D{File exists?}
    D -- No --> E[Print file-not-found error and exit]
    D -- Yes --> F[Set maximum line width to 70]
    F --> G[Build sed cleanup script]
    G --> H[Remove leading carets, tabs, and spaces]
    H --> I[Fold long lines at word boundaries]
    I --> J[Print formatted text]
    J --> K[Exit with pipeline status]
